data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! INVESTOR’s dream:This charming, fixer- upper is a 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, & a convenient 1.5 bath spanning 2 levels.A spacious living room w bay windows. Master bedroom  with a walk-in closet. A full bath w an oversize granite shower.The 1.5 bath is equally stylish w its granite countertops. The kitchen is equipped w granite countertops & pantry allowing your creativity to run wild w possibilities. Space is pre-wired w security system offering peace of mind.Appliances such as cooktop stove microwave & dishwasher are included in the kitchen. Washer & dryer connection.Parking is a breeze w this 1 car, garage and plenty of space for additional vehicles. The commercial grade garage door opener enhances security. Enjoy central air & heat making this property a promising investment opportunity. With some TLC & your personal touch. This home has the potential to shine. Don’t miss out contact us today to explore this fixer-upper’s incredible potential.
